channel.title: Force at witch Kedz
channel.description:
You may think what the fuck but this is serious issue.
Well you may think why does moparscape have so many people? Well its been answered after a few minutes of IRC chat and working out things. Moparscapers contain High amounts of Kedz (this is the metal that is attracted to Moparscape) But to know why they gather over Moparscape you have to work out the amount of Kedz each moparscaper has and the force they are attracted to. Magnetic force is measured in Tesla so we used that, The original formula was: F=BIL [quote=Stork from IRC]F is the force dragging them to mprscp, B is the mprscp field, I is the current density of mprscp, and L is the length of there moparpenis [/Quote]
So working from that and lots of other stuff I came up with this: F=BIL F=((B(3xClient.Java^X)(*/2))
B= Moparscape user total I= 3 time the size of there Client.java to the power of silab inteligence L= Total of all Penis size divided by 2 (Penis size is from 0.0007" to 1/2" of your lucky)
So the ratio of Kedz to Tesla is: 9876468435465432:1
It takes 1 Tesla to Lift 9876468435465432 and 1 Kedz is Six billion earth tonnes.
I'm going to have my lunch. Please tell me Anything I have missed (will write more in few mins)
WARNING: THIS IS NOT ACCURATE; I DID NOT TAKE INTO ACCOUNT THEIR RUNESCAPE ADDICTION, THERE OWN INTELLIGENCE, AND SPARE TIME
